const headHtml = "<title>Latest Hypixel SkyBlock Trends (June 2026)</title>\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"A data-backed June 2026 SkyBlock trend report covering fishing momentum after 0.25, market behavior shifts, patch cadence, and what players are focusing on now.\">\n    <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://notenoughcoins.net/guides/hypixel-skyblock-trends-june-2026\">\n\n    <meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://notenoughcoins.net/guides/hypixel-skyblock-trends-june-2026\">\n    <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\">\n    <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Latest Hypixel SkyBlock Trends (June 2026)\">\n    <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Trend radar for current SkyBlock: community focus, economy friction, and patch cadence visualized with practical actions.\">\n    <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://notenoughcoins.net/static/NEC.png\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BlogPosting\",\n        \"headline\": \"Latest Hypixel SkyBlock Trends (June 2026)\",\n        \"description\": \"June 2026 trend report for Hypixel SkyBlock based on patch notes and current community discussion.\",\n        \"datePublished\": \"2026-06-15\",\n        \"dateModified\": \"2026-06-15\",\n        \"author\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n          \"name\": \"NotEnoughCoins\"\n        },\n        \"publisher\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n          \"name\": \"Coflnet GmbH\"\n        },\n        \"url\": \"https://notenoughcoins.net/guides/hypixel-skyblock-trends-june-2026\"\n      }\n    </script>";
const bodyHtml = "<main>\n      <div class=\"site-shell article-layout\">\n        <article class=\"article\">\n          <a class=\"article-meta\" href=\"/guides#months-list\">Scheduled 2026-06-15 • Trend Report</a>\n          <h1>Latest Hypixel SkyBlock trends (June 2026)</h1>\n          <p class=\"lede\">This report tracks what moved most in the last month, not what made the loudest thumbnail. Right now, SkyBlock momentum is concentrated around fishing progression after 0.25, practical economy confusion (especially around bazaar pricing logic), and a clear appetite for better progression/flip tooling. The practical takeaway is to prioritize stable execution over hype spikes.</p>\n\n          <div class=\"note\">\n            <strong>Method:</strong> signal scoring combines official patch cadence plus current r/HypixelSkyblock post volume and engagement patterns. Scores are directional trend indicators, not exact market prices.\n          </div>\n\n          <h2>Trend momentum scoreboard</h2>\n          <p>The highest momentum trend is fishing progression content after Lotus Atoll. Economy-learning threads are the second strongest cluster, especially around pricing anomalies, bait value, and NPC-versus-bazaar decisions.</p>\n          <figure class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"trend-chart-title\">\n            <figcaption id=\"trend-chart-title\"><strong>Chart 1:</strong> June trend momentum score (0 to 100)</figcaption>\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 760 360\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Bar chart of SkyBlock trend momentum\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\">\n              <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"760\" height=\"360\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"/>\n              <line x1=\"120\" y1=\"50\" x2=\"120\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.25)\"/>\n              <line x1=\"120\" y1=\"300\" x2=\"700\" y2=\"300\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.25)\"/>\n\n              <text x=\"20\" y=\"90\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"14\">Fishing 0.25</text>\n              <rect x=\"120\" y=\"72\" width=\"532\" height=\"28\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#79e4b0\"/>\n              <text x=\"660\" y=\"90\" fill=\"#0b1126\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">92</text>\n\n              <text x=\"20\" y=\"138\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"14\">Economy QA</text>\n              <rect x=\"120\" y=\"120\" width=\"428\" height=\"28\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#8fd2ff\"/>\n              <text x=\"556\" y=\"138\" fill=\"#0b1126\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">74</text>\n\n              <text x=\"20\" y=\"186\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"14\">Tool Demand</text>\n              <rect x=\"120\" y=\"168\" width=\"395\" height=\"28\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#ffd166\"/>\n              <text x=\"523\" y=\"186\" fill=\"#0b1126\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">68</text>\n\n              <text x=\"20\" y=\"234\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"14\">Grind Friction</text>\n              <rect x=\"120\" y=\"216\" width=\"366\" height=\"28\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#ffb780\"/>\n              <text x=\"494\" y=\"234\" fill=\"#0b1126\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">63</text>\n\n              <text x=\"20\" y=\"282\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"14\">Security Risk</text>\n              <rect x=\"120\" y=\"264\" width=\"336\" height=\"28\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#ff8b8b\"/>\n              <text x=\"464\" y=\"282\" fill=\"#0b1126\" font-size=\"13\" font-weight=\"700\">58</text>\n            </svg>\n          </figure>\n\n          <h2>Patch cadence trend</h2>\n          <p>Patch spacing has stayed relatively fast from late April onward. That matters for traders because short release cycles increase temporary dislocations and reduce the shelf life of lazy “buy-and-forget” assumptions.</p>\n          <figure class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"cadence-chart-title\">\n            <figcaption id=\"cadence-chart-title\"><strong>Chart 2:</strong> days between major updates</figcaption>\n            <svg viewBox=\"0 0 760 320\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Line chart of days between recent major SkyBlock patches\" width=\"100%\" height=\"auto\">\n              <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"760\" height=\"320\" fill=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.02)\"/>\n              <line x1=\"90\" y1=\"40\" x2=\"90\" y2=\"270\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.25)\"/>\n              <line x1=\"90\" y1=\"270\" x2=\"700\" y2=\"270\" stroke=\"rgba(255,255,255,0.25)\"/>\n\n              <line x1=\"170\" y1=\"70\" x2=\"380\" y2=\"210\" stroke=\"#8fd2ff\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n              <line x1=\"380\" y1=\"210\" x2=\"590\" y2=\"100\" stroke=\"#8fd2ff\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n\n              <circle cx=\"170\" cy=\"70\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#79e4b0\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"380\" cy=\"210\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#79e4b0\"/>\n              <circle cx=\"590\" cy=\"100\" r=\"8\" fill=\"#79e4b0\"/>\n\n              <text x=\"142\" y=\"292\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">0.24.3→0.24.4</text>\n              <text x=\"350\" y=\"292\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">0.24.4→0.24.5</text>\n              <text x=\"548\" y=\"292\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">0.24.5→0.25</text>\n\n              <text x=\"160\" y=\"58\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">28d</text>\n              <text x=\"372\" y=\"198\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">8d</text>\n              <text x=\"582\" y=\"88\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">22d</text>\n\n              <text x=\"18\" y=\"76\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">30</text>\n              <text x=\"18\" y=\"142\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">20</text>\n              <text x=\"18\" y=\"208\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">10</text>\n              <text x=\"18\" y=\"274\" fill=\"#d9e2ff\" font-size=\"13\">0</text>\n            </svg>\n          </figure>\n\n          <h2>What these trends mean for players right now</h2>\n          <ul class=\"related-list\">\n            <li>Fishing route mastery beats blind rarity chasing. The winning players are optimizing chapter flow and uptime, not just praying for one high-roll catch.</li>\n            <li>Economy confusion is still a profit source. If you understand fill speed, replacement pools, and event pressure, you benefit from mispricing waves.</li>\n            <li>Tool usage is no longer optional at scale. More players are asking for risk scoring, fill estimates, progression suggestions, and alerting.</li>\n            <li>Security hygiene is an actual meta issue. Account-loss posts still spike, so secure mod workflow matters as much as strategy quality.</li>\n          </ul>\n\n          <h2>Rich media snapshot: trend evidence matrix</h2>\n          <div class=\"note\">\n            <table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse: collapse; color: #dbe4ff;\">\n              <thead>\n                <tr>\n                  <th style=\"text-align:left; padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">Trend</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align:left; padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">Signal examples</th>\n                  <th style=\"text-align:left; padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);\">Action</th>\n                </tr>\n              </thead>\n              <tbody>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Fishing progression spike</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Lotus Atoll reaction threads and trophy-frog route discussion</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Prioritize chapter flow + repeatable catch uptime</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Bazaar confusion</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">NPC vs bazaar sell questions, bait value complaints, spread anomalies</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Use live demand + margin tools before committing volume</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Tool demand growth</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Community requests for progression/flip assistants</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);\">Build a personal dashboard stack and standard checklist</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem;\">Time-friction and wipe anxiety</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem;\">High-engagement complaint and wipe posts</td>\n                  <td style=\"padding: 0.55rem;\">Reduce risk: secure mod sources, diversify coin methods</td>\n                </tr>\n              </tbody>\n            </table>\n          </div>\n\n          <h2>Practical 7-day strategy</h2>\n          <p>If you want to align with current trends without overreacting, use this sequence: lock in stable money method first, add one fishing progression block per session, track top movers once per day instead of every hour, and only scale capital where volume confirms your thesis.</p>\n\n          <h2>Read next</h2>\n          <ul class=\"related-list\">\n            <li><a href=\"/guides/hypixel-skyblock-0-25-lotus-atoll-update\">Hypixel SkyBlock 0.25 Lotus Atoll Update Guide</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"/guides/market-literacy-margin-volume-risk\">How to Read Margin, Volume and Risk Before You Flip</a></li>\n            <li><a href=\"/guides/flipping-tools-comparison-2026\">Best Hypixel SkyBlock Flipping Tools Compared in 2026</a></li>\n          </ul>\n        </article>\n\n        <aside class=\"article-aside\">\n          <div>\n            <h3>Trend tracking tools</h3>\n            <ul class=\"tool-list\">\n              <li><a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/topMovers\">SkyCofl top movers</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://sky.coflnet.com/bazaar\">SkyCofl bazaar</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://pro.skyblock.bz/features/market-trends\">BazaarPro market trends</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://bazaartracker.com/demand\">BazaarTracker demand</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://bazaartracker.com/margin\">BazaarTracker margin</a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <h3>Primary sources</h3>\n            <ul class=\"tool-list\">\n              <li><a href=\"https://hypixel.net/forums/skyblock-patch-notes.158/\">Hypixel SkyBlock Patch Notes</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://old.reddit.com/r/HypixelSkyblock/top/?sort=top&t=month\">r/HypixelSkyblock top month</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://old.reddit.com/r/HypixelSkyblock/search?q=fishing&restrict_sr=on&sort=new&t=month\">r/HypixelSkyblock fishing threads</a></li>\n              <li><a href=\"https://old.reddit.com/r/HypixelSkyblock/search?q=bazaar&restrict_sr=on&sort=new&t=month\">r/HypixelSkyblock bazaar threads</a></li>\n            </ul>\n          </div>\n          <div>\n            <h3>Scope note</h3>\n            <p>Charts in this report are trend signals from current public discussion and patch cadence, not promises of guaranteed profit or fixed rates.</p>\n          </div>\n        </aside>\n      </div>\n    </main>";
